data.description: WATERFRONT HOME on canal to Lake Pierce!  BOAT HOUSE WITH ELECTRIC LIFT, boat ramp, cleaning station plus large storage room. Solid and well  maintained, this home offers spacious comfort. 2 full bedrooms with walk-in closets plus a den/ extra bedroom, open kitchen/ dining area, inside laundry and a huge great room with a wood burning fireplace & a wall of built-in cabinet/ book shelves.  Some cosmetic touches required to lighten and brighten, but the possibilities are endless.  Enjoy the screened front porch and the convenience of the one car garage with a separate but attached storage room and all of the extra driveway space. The owner has kept the home in good condition adding a new roof (2020), AC (2022).  NO HOA, just nature to enjoy.  Do not let the days on the market stop you.  This may be just the right home for you!
